The evidence with the title 'Behind Carly Fiorina's 30,000 HP layoffs - sep. 21, 2015 ' says Sep 21, 2015  ... Carly Fiorina's disastrous decision to merge with Compaq in 2002 led to nearly 30000 layoffs at the company.  ... Some 30,000 layoffs at Hewlett-Packard during her tenure as ceo.  ... Later in 2001, HP laid off 7,500 employees. 
